(120, 'Chugyeokja', '(2008)', 'Action, Crime, Thriller', '7.8', 'A disgraced ex-policeman who runs a small ring of prostitutes finds himself in a race against time when one of his women goes missing.', 'Na Hong-jin', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1190539/?ref_=adv_li_tt', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNWI0ZTEyZTQtZDNjOS00OTg4LTkyNGQtOTJiMmM3MDk5MjFmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTMxODk2OTU@._V1_UY98_CR1,0,67,98_AL_.jpg', '120.jpeg'),
