(304, 'J?b? ninp?chô', '(1993)', 'Animation, Action, Adventure', '7.9', 'A vagabond swordsman is aided by a beautiful ninja girl and a crafty spy in confronting a demonic clan of killers - with a ghost from his past as their leader - who are bent on overthrowing the Tokugawa Shogunate.', 'Yoshiaki Kawajiri', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0107692/?ref_=adv_li_tt', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTMyZGI4N2YtMzdkNi00MDZmLTg4NmItMzg0ODY5NjdhZjYwL2ltYWdlL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzM4MjM0Nzg@._V1_UY98_CR1,0,67,98_AL_.jpg', '304.jpeg'),
