(790, 'Girl, Interrupted', '(1999)', 'Biography, Drama', '7.3', 'Based on writer Susanna Kaysen\'s account of her 18-month stay at a mental hospital in the late 1960s.', 'James Mangold', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0172493/?ref_=adv_li_tt', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzdjZDYwM2QtMGNlZS00MGQzLTlhMjctYTU4NWI5MWJlYmQwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTAwMzUyOTc@._V1.jpg', '790.jpeg'),
