(793, 'The People vs. Larry Flynt', '(1996)', 'Biography, Drama', '7.3', 'The story of controversial pornography publisher Larry Flynt, and how he became a defender of free speech.', 'Milos Forman', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0117318/?ref_=adv_li_tt', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTY3NjA3OTY2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjAyNjQxMTE@._V1.jpg', '793.jpeg'),
