(2164, 'Trolljegeren', '(2010)', 'Drama, Fantasy, Horror', '7.0', 'A group of students investigates a series of mysterious bear killings, but learns that there are much more dangerous things going on. They start to follow a mysterious hunter, learning that he is actually a troll hunter.', 'André ?vredal', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1740707/?ref_=adv_li_tt', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTkyMTgxNzIwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjYyNjM5NA@@._V1.jpg', '2164.jpeg'),
