(2175, 'Le pacte des loups', '(2001)', 'Action, Adventure, Drama', '7.0', 'In 18th-century France, the Chevalier de Fronsac and his Native American friend Mani are sent to the Gevaudan province at the king\'s behest to investigate the killings of hundreds by a mysterious beast.', 'Christophe Gans', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0237534/?ref_=adv_li_tt', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTkxMjg5MDYtZDkyMS00NjFlLTk5YTItMWUyOTNkOTg4YmRhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDk3NzU2MTQ@._V1.jpg', '2175.jpeg'),
