(3550, 'Full Metal Jacket', '(1987)', 'Drama, War', '8.3', 'A pragmatic U.S. Marine observes the dehumanizing effects the Vietnam War has on his fellow recruits from their brutal boot camp training to the bloody street fighting in Hue.', 'Stanley Kubrick', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0093058/?ref_=adv_li_tt', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzkxODk0NjEtYjc4Mi00ZDI0LTgyYjEtYzc1NDkxY2YzYTgyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzkwMjQ5NzM@._V1.jpg', '3550.jpeg'),
