(3555, 'Mandariinid', '(2013)', 'Drama, War', '8.2', 'In 1992, war rages in Abkhazia, a breakaway region of Georgia. An Estonian man Ivo has decided to stay behind and harvest his crops of tangerines. In a bloody conflict at his door, a wounded man is left behind, and Ivo takes him in.', 'Zaza Urushadze', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2991224/?ref_=adv_li_tt', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTgwNzA3MDQzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTE5MDE5NDE@._V1.jpg', '3555.jpeg'),
