(3802, 'News of the World', '(2020)', 'Action, Adventure, Drama', '6.8', 'A Civil War veteran agrees to deliver a girl, taken by the Kiowa people years ago, to her aunt and uncle, against her will. They travel hundreds of miles and face grave dangers as they search for a place that either can call home.', 'Paul Greengrass', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt6878306/?ref_=adv_li_tt', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDNlNmVlNDItMjE3Yi00ZTA3LWIyOTktNDhhMGFlZjk5ZDQ0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDM2NDM2MQ@@._V1.jpg', '3802.jpeg'),
